  "grammar": [
    {"id":"g01","title":"“您”的基本用法","titleEn":"The basic use of nín","explanation":"“您”是“你”的敬称，常用于对长辈、老师或需要表示尊敬的人。","examples":[{"hanzi":"老师，您好！","pinyin":"Lǎoshī, nín hǎo!","english":"Hello, teacher!","highlight":["您"]}],"formula":{"pattern":"你好 → 您好","patternEn":"Replace 你 with 您 to make the greeting polite","note":"先学习“你好”，把“你”换成“您”，就是对老师或需要尊敬的人的礼貌说法。","noteEn":"Start with 你好. Replace 你 with 您 to greet a teacher or a respected person politely."}},
    {"id":"g02","title":"后缀“们”的基本用法","titleEn":"The plural suffix men","explanation":"“们”用在代词或指人的名词后面表示复数。","examples":[{"hanzi":"同学们、你们、学生们。","pinyin":"Tóngxuémen, nǐmen, xuéshengmen.","english":"Classmates, you, students.","highlight":["们"]}],"formula":{"pattern":"人称代词或人的名词 + 们","patternEn":"Personal pronoun or person noun + men","note":"用于指一组人。","noteEn":"Use it to refer to a group of people."}}
  ],
